#           - Dialog: dialog_list, confirmation
#           - Scoreboard: add, trigger
#           - Trigger
#
#   Folge 36: Handelsfenster: Clear + Macros + Storage + Scoreboards = Werte in Verkauf dynamisch anpassen
#       Themen:
#           - Scoreboards: add, reset
#           - Trigger
#           - Macros
#           - Storage
#           - Clear
